29
00:06:58.034 --> 00:07:00.912
<i>I really relived what happened.</i>

30
00:08:03.391 --> 00:08:08.563
It's hard to recognize, but it was here.

31
00:08:12.567 --> 00:08:14.610
They burned people here.

32
00:08:14.944 --> 00:08:17.613
A lot of people were burned here.

33
00:08:28.457 --> 00:08:30.877
Yes, this is the place.

34
00:09:07.455 --> 00:09:11.125
No one ever left here again.

35
00:09:18.716 --> 00:09:21.052
The gas vans came in here...

36
00:09:21.302 --> 00:09:23.930
There were two huge ovens,

37
00:09:27.141 --> 00:09:31.145
