89
00:15:40.889 --> 00:15:43.809
<i>because he never thought he'd survive,</i>

90
00:15:44.184 --> 00:15:47.021
<i>but... he's alive.</i>

91
00:15:51.775 --> 00:15:54.320
Why does he smile all the time?

92
00:16:03.912 --> 00:16:05.914
<i>What do you want him to do... cry?</i>

93
00:16:06.248 --> 00:16:08.250
<i>Sometimes you smile, sometimes you cry.</i>

94
00:16:10.210 --> 00:16:12.838
