173
00:26:50.850 --> 00:26:53.395
ITZHAK DUGIN:
Survivor of Vilna


174
00:27:15.667 --> 00:27:18.503
<i>They'd been in the earth 4 months,</i>

175
00:27:18.586 --> 00:27:20.964
<i>and it was winter.</i>

176
00:27:21.047 --> 00:27:22.882
<i>They were very well preserved.</i>

177
00:27:22.966 --> 00:27:26.761
