191
00:29:38.309 --> 00:29:40.895
With just their hands?

192
00:30:04.669 --> 00:30:06.921
<i>When we first opened the graves,</i>

193
00:30:07.005 --> 00:30:10.467
<i>we couldn't help it,
we all burst out sobbing.</i>


194
00:30:10.550 --> 00:30:15.305
<i>But the Germans almost beat us to death.</i>

195
00:30:15.388 --> 00:30:19.184
<i>We had to work
at a killing pace for two days,</i>


196
00:30:19.267 --> 00:30:22.020
<i>beaten all the time, and with no tools.</i>

197
00:30:23.730 --> 00:30:25.940
They all burst out sobbing?

198
00:30:48.588 --> 00:30:51.049
<i>The Germans even forbade us</i>

199
00:30:51.132 --> 00:30:54.677
<i>to use the words
