203
00:31:18.535 --> 00:31:23.623
<i>The Germans made us
refer to the bodies as “F (guren,</i> ”


204
00:31:23.706 --> 00:31:26.543
<i>that is, as puppets, as dolls,</i>

205
00:31:27.794 --> 00:31:29.921
