208
00:31:53.528 --> 00:31:56.489
<i>The head of the Vilna Gestapo told us,</i>

209
00:31:56.573 --> 00:32:00.201
<i>“There are 90,000 people lying there,</i>

210
00:32:00.285 --> 00:32:03.329
<i>and absolutely no trace
